13:39.786 --> 13:41.020 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
MARCIA COYLE: Yes.

13:41.120 --> 13:42.555 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And we're just
