13:47.460 --> 13:52.065 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And now let's
look in depth
at Justice Scalia's legacy, not
what's next,

13:52.165 --> 13:53.966 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
