language and thinking,
right?

24:38.744 --> 24:41.280 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY ROSEN: Well, it's
spectacular, and
also because it taught me to
pronounce it.

24:41.380 --> 24:43.949 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
