Pyramid. But
it's Cheops' Pyramid.

24:44.049 --> 24:44.416 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: Cheops.

24:44.516 --> 24:45.617 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

24:45.718 --> 24:47.453 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY ROSEN: I learned that
from looking
it up.

24:47.553 --> 24:48.921 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Well, I will tell
you, I was
sure that that was a reference
to the Great

24:49.021 --> 24:49.888 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
Pyramid. And I was right.

24:49.988 --> 24:51.690 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

24:51.790 --> 24:52.424 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY ROSEN: Well, absolutely.
No, this
was a smaller one that he was
really talking

24:52.524 --> 24:52.991 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
about.

24:53.092 --> 24:54.893 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
JEFFREY BROWN: OK.

24:54.993 --> 24:56.895 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY ROSEN: No, but the fact
