25:15.614 --> 25:19.752 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
It was just he was a deeply
literate man who
had such a joy in writing, was
such a beautiful

25:19.852 --> 25:23.989 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
writer, the greatest since
