25:24.089 --> 25:27.259 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
are so memorable made him the
influential
justice that he was.

25:27.359 --> 25:30.996 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Very briefly, did
