impact on the law?

25:31.096 --> 25:32.931 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
EDWARD WHELAN: OH, absolutely.

25:33.031 --> 25:38.070 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
As Jeff has mentioned, he really
transformed
the approach that the court has
taken and

25:38.170 --> 25:43.108 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
