recognize the
deep wisdom there. And law
students will read

26:08.233 --> 26:12.271 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
his opinions as long as anyone
reads Supreme
Court cases.

26:12.371 --> 26:14.606 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: And I will ask
you for a brief
last word on that, too.

26:14.706 --> 26:21.113 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
