the day.

26:21.213 --> 26:22.948 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
ELIZABETH WYDRA: Absolutely.

26:23.048 --> 26:26.318 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
So, his legacy will be his focus
on the text
and history of Constitution, but
there were

26:26.418 --> 26:30.589 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
many cases in which progressives
showed that
the text and history of the
Constitution supported

26:30.689 --> 26:34.460 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
