equality cases, where he simply
is on the

26:34.560 --> 26:36.361 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
wrong side of history there, in
my opinion.

26:36.462 --> 26:40.232 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Elizabeth Wydra,
Ed Whelan
and Jeffrey Rosen, thank you,
all three, very

26:40.332 --> 26:40.899 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
much.

26:40.999 --> 26:41.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
EDWARD WHELAN: Thank you.

