improving the
relationship.

49:43.447 --> 49:49.053 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
That includes a series of
community events
on issues about the Henrietta
Lacks story,

49:49.153 --> 49:54.058 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
