cooperation with the

49:59.196 --> 50:20.417 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Lacks family and they address
the ethical
issues related to biomedical
research.

50:20.517 --> 50:24.822 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Finally tonight, we close with
an unusual
work of art about Antonin
Scalia.

50:24.922 --> 50:30.995 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Last year, the Arena Stage
theater here in
Washington put on a production
of "The Originalist,"

50:31.095 --> 50:33.697 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
